ader\", \"from\": 2391, \"to\": 2405}, {\"ngram\": \"a corner\", \"from\": 2411, \"to\": 2419}, {\"ngram\": \"a sizzling move\", \"from\": 2451, \"to\": 2466}, {\"ngram\": \"the third\", \"from\": 2476, \"to\": 2485}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Getty Images: Alex Livesey) Brand was then rewarded for her Player of the Match performance four minutes later, tapping home a slicing low cross that rifled in behind the Matildas' scrambling back-line.\", \"from\": 2486, \"to\": 2690, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2501, \"end\": 2505, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\", \"score\": 0.9999999998144631, \"rank\": 1.42159663852927e-10, \"text\": \"Alex\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Rousseau\"}, {\"begin\": 2506, \"end\": 2513, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Warne_Livesey\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8065337815822074e-21, \"text\": \"Livesey\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Warne_Livesey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Warne_Livesey\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"(Getty Images\", \"from\": 2486, \"to\": 2499}, {\"ngram\": \"her Player\", \"from\": 2543, \"to\": 2553}, {\"ngram\": \"the Match performance\", \"from\": 2557, \"to\": 2578}, {\"ngram\": \"a slicing low cross\", \"from\": 2612, \"to\": 2631}, {\"ngram\": \"the Matildas\", \"from\": 2654, \"to\": 2666}, {\"ngram\": \"back-line\", \"from\": 2679, \"to\": 2688}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Germans could have had a fourth goal not long afterwards, bundling the ball over the line in a scramble in the box, but the linesperson correctly flagged the play as being offside.\", \"from\": 2692, \"to\": 2876, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2696, \"end\": 2703, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nazi_Germany\", \"score\": 0.9998944100841851, \"rank\": 0.00010527013059375178, \"text\": \"Germans\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"],